    runtime stack:
01-01 23:15:29.409  25930-25930/com.example.hello E/Go﹕ runtime.gothrow(0x5e8502b0, 0x2a)
01-01 23:15:29.409  25930-25930/com.example.hello E/Go﹕ /usr/local/go/src/runtime/panic.go:504 +0x8c
